{"story":{"group_1":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_film_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20171.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":1,"pos":2,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime02","chara":[{"id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-1"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Magical Girls...@I had no idea they actually existed...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":250301,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-2"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I was surprised, too."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":250301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-3"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I didn't expect a classmate of mine@to have Magical Girl potential..."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"motion":0,"pos":0,"posX":-50,"posY":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-4"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It's not really that rare of a thing."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-5"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]There seem to be other students at@your school that also have potential."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-6"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So, um..."},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-7"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Is it really true that, if you become@a Magical Girl, you get your wish granted?"},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-8"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Yes. As long as you make a contract@with me."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Hm...hmmm...."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-10"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]A wish, huh...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-11"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]When you put it that way, all kinds@of desires pop up in my head..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-12"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Ohh...@I-I can't decide..."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Every Magical Girl has different potential,@which corresponds with their wish's effects."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-14"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]With extremely high magical potential,@it's even possible to alter history."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-15"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But your potential is...a little lower@than average."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-16"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Lower than average...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":100,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Even so, your wish should still have value."},{"chara":[{"id":250301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-18"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It's a miracle brought about by magic,@after all."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-19"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]A miracle..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Of course, fighting Witches means@putting your life at stake."},{"chara":[{"id":250301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-21"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So you should think about it carefully@before making the decision."},{"chara":[{"id":250301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-22"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If you'd like, you can come see what@it's like to fight a Witch first, and..."},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-23"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Ah, no."},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-24"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I've already decided."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913001-002-25"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Decided on what...?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"deleteArmatureList":[1],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
